    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional throttle response. The power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanical highlights include a documented subframe reinforcement and a recent VANOS bulletproofing, ensuring structural and valvetrain longevity. The suspension retains its telepathic feedback via refreshed control arm bushings and performance-valved dampers. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina consistent with its 'good' status, the drivetrain remains robust with linear power delivery up to the 8,000 RPM redline. A mechanically sorted, driver-spec example for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
