    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW 540i xDrive represents a sophisticated blend of executive luxury and spirited performance. The exterior, finished in Bluestone Metallic, retains a deep luster, showing only minor, expected road wear on the front fascia. The cabin is an oasis of comfort, featuring Mocha Dakota leather seats that remain supple and free of any significant creasing or wear. Every electronic component, from the intuitive iDrive 6.0 system with navigation to the multi-zone climate control, operates exactly as intended. Under the hood, the 3.0L TwinPower Turbo inline-six engine runs exceptionally smooth, benefiting from a rigorous service history and a very recent synthetic oil change. The 19-inch wheels are wrapped in high-tread Pirelli Cinturato P7 tires, ensuring a quiet and controlled ride. This vehicle has been a non-smoker car, kept in a climate-controlled garage, and comes with a complete set of service records and two keys. It is a solid, well-maintained example of German engineering ready for immediate enjoyment.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
